                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850629-54-off257 t17850629-54-crimeloc259"></join> I saw three or four lurking persons, about eleven in the forenoon , the prisoner at the bar gave me some suspicion of him, I felt in my pocket and found my handkerchief was gone; I pursued the prisoner at the bar, and saw him throw it away before I took him.</p>
               <p>- MASTERS sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw him take the handkerchief from the prosecutor.</p>
